strings: <voice_0x01001574><se_def>awesome!: Anonymous<:> What are you doing! , let me go!
<voice_0x01001575><se_def>awesome!: If you... if they don't get in your way... I can get Rapthorn's full power...
<voice_0x01001576><se_def>awesome!: But... it's already over... you've lost hope...
<voice_0x01001577><se_def>awesome!: leave me I need your help!
<voice_0x01001578><se_def>China: I'm not gonna let you die, Zhao
<voice_0x01001579><se_def>China: Live in the knowledge that the brother you hated all your life will have mercy on you.
<voice_0x0100157A><se_def>China: I don't want to leave them all behind.
<voice_0x0100157B><se_def>awesome!: Are you insulting me again?
<voice_0x0100157D><se_def>China: About 10 years ago I lost my family and about ten years ago I came to the temple for the first time.
<voice_0x0100157E><se_def>China: You're the first person I'll speak to.
<voice_0x0100157F><se_def>China: I have nothing left, no family, no home...
<voice_0x01001580><se_def>China: you were nice to me i was good from the beginning
<voice_0x01001581><se_def>China: Knowing who I am changes everything...
<voice_0x01001582><se_def>China: But I will never forget this grace.
<voice_0x01001583><se_def>awesome!: You're going to regret the day you saved my life.
<voice_0x01001584><se_def>China: I don't mind. No matter how ugly you are, you can't hurt me anymore.
<voice_0x01001586><se_def>China: Rings fit women?
<voice_0x01001587><se_def>awesome!: Now he's yours and he means nothing to me
<voice_0x01001588><se_high>Accuracy: angel face
<voice_0x01001589><se_high>Accuracy: Let him go, he's in a lot of pain.
